The '''[[2014–15 NHL season|2014–15]] [[Columbus Blue Jackets]] [[season (sports)|season]]''' was the [[List of Columbus Blue Jackets seasons|15th]] season for the [[National Hockey League]] franchise that was established on June 25, 1997.<ref>{{cite book |last=National Hockey League|title=The National Hockey League Official Guide & Record Book/2014|year=2013 |publisher= Diamond Sports Data, Inc. |page=49|isbn= 978-1-894801-26-3}}</ref> The Blue Jackets missed the playoffs despite qualifying the previous year. The Blue Jackets finished strong, going 15-1-1 in their final 17 games.

