;Draft notes

* {{ref label|Note1|a|a}}The [[Detroit Red Wings]]' third-round pick went to the [[Columbus Blue Jackets]] as the result of a trade on June 28, 2014 that sent Edmonton's third-round pick in 2014 (63rd overall) to Detroit in exchange for a third-round pick in [[2015 NHL Entry Draft|2015]] and this pick.<ref name="2014DraftDay2">{{cite web|url=http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=724266|title=Notes from the 2014 NHL Draft|date=June 28, 2014|accessdate=June 28, 2014}}</ref>
* {{ref label|Note1|b|b}}The [[Columbus Blue Jackets]]' fifth-round pick was re-acquired as the result of a trade on June 25, 2014 that sent [[Nikita Nikitin]] to Edmonton in exchange for this pick.<ref>{{cite web|title=Oilers Acquire D Nikitin from Blue Jackets for Pick|url=https://www.tsn.ca/nhl/story/?id=455660|accessdate=June 25, 2014|date=June 25, 2014}}</ref><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Edmonton previously acquired this pick as the result of a trade March 5, 2014 that sent [[Nick Schultz]] to Columbus in exchange for this pick.<ref>{{cite web|title=Blue Jackets obtain Nick Schultz from Oilers: report|url=http://www.nhl.com/ice/blogpost.htm?id=26848|publisher=National Hockey League|date=March 5, 2014|accessdate=March 5, 2014}}</ref>
* The [[Columbus Blue Jackets]]' sixth-round pick went to the [[Minnesota Wild]] as the result of a trade on June 30, 2013 that sent [[Justin Falk]] to the New York Rangers in exchange for [[Benn Ferriero]] and this pick.<ref>{{cite web|title=Wild, Rangers swap Falk, Ferriero|url=http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=675768&navid=DL|publisher=[[National Hockey League]]|accessdate=June 30, 2013|date=June 30, 2013}}</ref><br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;New York previously acquired this pick as the result of a trade on April 3, 2013 that sent [[Marián Gáborík|Marian Gaborik]], [[Blake Parlett]] and [[Steven Delisle]] to Columbus in exchange for [[Derick Brassard]], [[Derek Dorsett]], [[John Moore (ice hockey)|John Moore]] and this pick.<ref>{{cite web|title=Kekalainen injects life into Blue Jackets with Gaborik|url=http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=663849|publisher=[[National Hockey League]]|accessdate=April 3, 2013|date=April 3, 2013}}</ref>

